Package: BioLogical
Type: Package
Title: a universal logical-based analysis framework of biological complex systems
Version: 0.1.17
Author: Yao Yuxiang
Maintainer: Yao Yuxiang <y.x.yao@foxmail.com>
Description: BioLogical, a user-friendly package, designed for analyzing foundational properties of universal logical systems. It can analyze logical paradigms, calculate order parameters, convert system frameworks, and simulate discrete dynamic systems.
License: GPL-3 + MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.10), 
         ggplot2 (>= 3.4.0)
Suggests: igraph
LinkingTo: Rcpp
